,"msg":"本人做貓酒店, 本身有7隻貓, 睇你話柯血但好活躍應該都係D糧唔岩佢食, 貓糧要慢慢試, 建議你唔好一次過買咁多, 要搵到夾你貓貓既都好講運架, 另外如果嚴重既情況呢, 例如尿道果邊問題,就會見到佢成日走入廁所咩都柯唔出,淨係柯血定會滴出黎, 但就唔係你依家既情況. 如果你想試我既貓糧可以PM我既"},{"pid":"6ed7e9f51581abffa9e9f2a1f832f290c034f011","tid":765901,"uid":35924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T11:06:56.000Z","msg":"平時食開濕定乾？"},{"pid":"65c9cb12c4e2b9c02b3583db680cff33cdd985bb","tid":765901,"uid":183826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ed7e9f51581abffa9e9f2a1f832f290c034f011","tid":765901,"uid":35924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T11:06:56.000Z","msg":"平時食開濕定乾？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T12:21:20.000Z","msg":"乾糧啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6ed60b6c21123e38264498c3eddbb10ab5fb545","tid":765901,"uid":35924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65c9cb12c4e2b9c02b3583db680cff33cdd985bb","tid":765901,"uid":183826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ed7e9f51581abffa9e9f2a1f832f290c034f011","tid":765901,"uid":35924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T11:06:56.000Z","msg":"平時食開濕定乾？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T12:21:20.000Z","msg":"乾糧啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T15:01:45.000Z","msg":"試下每餐餵少d 乾，大個d再間中餵下濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n貓仔咁細好易消化不良"},{"pid":"8acdc281bc5d0087b504e1808efe2621f7cacdeb","tid":765901,"uid":183826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6ed60b6c21123e38264498c3eddbb10ab5fb545","tid":765901,"uid":35924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65c9cb12c4e2b9c02b3583db680cff33cdd985bb","tid":765901,"uid":183826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ed7e9f51581abffa9e9f2a1f832f290c034f011","tid":765901,"uid":35924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T11:06:56.000Z","msg":"平時食開濕定乾？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-0